Introduction

IS:SUE is a Japanese girl group formed under LAPONE GIRLS. The group comprises members Rin, Nano, Yuuki, and Rino. They gained recognition after participating in PRODUCE 101 JAPAN THE GIRLS in 2023.

On June 19, 2024, IS:SUE made their official debut with their first single, “1st IS:SUE.” Additionally, they expanded their reach by releasing a Korean version of their track “CONNECT.”
